{"tid":819716,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真post] 淺淡 ppi(Pixels per inch)，同iPhone Xr","createTime":"2018-09-15T04:37:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T17:18:38.000Z","uid":7109,"like":65,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"39945529e29203e9f1daa9ba41130056aa69c6cd","tid":819716,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:37:49.000Z","msg":"見到另一個POST講梗iPhone Xr 螢幕質素問題，好多人都屌Xr個mon好差，因為ppi唔高。<br />\n但發覺原來連登仔對ppi嘅概念唔太了解。當然好多萬能嘅連登仔們可能一早就知，點都好可以睇埋落去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：有D怕認真post冇人理<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">ppi(pixels per inch)</span>，係像素密度嘅單位，代表一英寸之內有幾多粒像素。一般而言，Ppi越高，螢幕顯示圖像就更精細。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/122549_7db5746ec50b686b99cf7ef4f96dc284.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F122549_7db5746ec50b686b99cf7ef4f96dc284.png&h=d2f4b5d1&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n圖中見到，20ppi嘅圖像比10ppi更加「精細」：你會更加感覺到呢個係一個圓型。<br />\n<br />\nppi嘅值同螢幕大小及解像度有關，點計算就唔詳細講了。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">問題嚟啦，既然ppi越高，圖像就越精細，咁係咪代表ppi越高越好呢？<br />\n答案：部分正確。</span><br />\n<br />\n跟據Apple所講，人眼無法喺一般使用<span style=\"color: red;\">手機</span>距離之下，「分辨」到300ppi 以上嘅螢幕。意思係無論個<span style=\"color: red;\">手機</span>螢幕係400ppi定320ppi，對你嚟講係無分別嘅，因為你跟本分辨唔到兩者有咩唔同。<br />\n姐係話，手機螢幕ppi越高越好，但超過300ppi的話，可以話係於你無別。<br />\n <br />\n點解我要highlight「手機」呢？因為300ppi並唔係任何螢幕ppi嘅標準，只適用於手機：<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/122832_0680951957de461d8330a06dd5b73d1b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F122832_0680951957de461d8330a06dd5b73d1b.png&h=d3ce7563&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n以iPad同iPhone做例子。因為iPhone 螢幕細過iPad好多，我地通常會近D睇iPhone，遠D睇iPad。所以iPhone 嘅 ppi 一般會高過iPad 。<br />\n<br />\n另一個例子就係 iPad(pro) 同iPad mini。因為iPad mini個螢幕細過 iPad(Pro) 好多，我地會比較近D睇iPad mini，而iPad(Pro) 就遠D睇。所以 iPad mini 嘅 ppi 會達到 iPhone 8 水平，而iPad(Pro)就唔達300ppi。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/122945_3a99a3d836cdb89f2e4d3a8d97116ef8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F122945_3a99a3d836cdb89f2e4d3a8d97116ef8.jpeg&h=5c443bb7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n正如電視/電腦螢幕，我地通常離電視1-2 m 咁樣睇，己經冇辦法見到佢起粒粒，我地唔需要整到電視/電腦螢幕達手機級嘅ppi。一方面無需要（使用距離遠，我地無法分辨），另一方面會提升成本，縮細螢幕大小等等。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">小總結，一般而言：<br />\n螢幕嘅使用距離越遠，ppi嘅需求越低。螢幕嘅螢幕越大，使用距離越遠。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">咁點解依加無論android 定 iOS，D螢幕ppi都係大過300 ，有D更加去到400幾呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n好大程度上係因為依加D電話鐘意玩鬥高spec，CPU 要2.8 GHz⋯⋯RAM要8GB⋯⋯ROM要512GB⋯⋯鬥完機內就鬥機外，個screen要4K，要6&rdquo;先夠⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n舉個例，同樣係5.5&rdquo;moon，Sony Z5 Premium 達到3840x2160 ( 806ppi)，而iPhone 8+ 都只係有 1920x1080(401ppi)，足足少一半（手機廠商傾向放幾種特定解像度落電話到，正如sony 放4K，Apple放2K，唔係以ppi做首要考慮條件）。<br />\n<br />\n但諗深一層，我地平時跟本唔能夠分辦到401ppi 同 806 ppi 嘅電話螢幕。放一個4K mon 落電話到，有用咩？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">iPhone Xr</span><br />\niPhone Xr 嘅ppi的確係比同樣大小嘅機輸蝕，6.1&rdquo;mon只有326 ppi，而5.5&rdquo;mon (Plus系列) 一早就有401ppi。但實際上，就一般使用而言，我地同樣係無能力分辨到326ppi同401ppi有咩分別，喺ppi上iPhone Xr 維持到一般水準嘅螢幕質素，而佢更加唔係720p(有機會下次解釋)。由iPhone 4S 開始己經用梗326ppi做標準，點解今時今日先會話佢粒粒mon？結論：iPhone Xr喺ppi上並無輸蝕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果小妹有地方講錯的話歡迎指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"7eb63ff850573515f6953a701a1fa048abed78a6","tid":819716,"uid":7109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會無人理？不安"},{"pid":"639121644bbfb05340db29f4d0ba39e610cb6b13","tid":819716,"uid":134665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80e941615037a350e7db7abd75d8816f8f8a982","tid":819716,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"639121644bbfb05340db29f4d0ba39e610cb6b13","tid":819716,"uid":134665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc1284c3b1f818fe358278ff214949bed2c38d3","tid":819716,"uid":182286,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:57:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c41741a4bfa59936a9ad603a2f98400b6fe6b606","tid":819716,"uid":119173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主認真 post 無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca6a67d74fab5f3c621b31e7e83ca37a0d067d0","tid":819716,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T05:11:22.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"98f5ed504dd24c8249afb66288bd1786ad390955","tid":819716,"uid":35347,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T05:11:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mostly-tech.com/2013/11/08/debunking-the-retina-display-myth/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmostly-tech.com%2F2013%2F11%2F08%2Fdebunking-the-retina-display-myth%2F&d=XHq8fknx0xpBd2vv980h4%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=981855c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://mostly-tech.com/2013/11/08/debunking-the-retina-display-myth/</a><br />\nApple個講法未必真<br />\n正如有人話人眼淨係睇到30fps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf42d70d3c52bd0d65a40773e6589b125becddfd","tid":819716,"uid":36231,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9cc1284c3b1f818fe358278ff214949bed2c